    "description": "Order-of-accuracy verification of the finite-volume Navier-Stokes solver using the method of manufactured solutions on a sequence of five systematically refined meshes. Expected second-order convergence in velocity and pressure norms is required to pass. Activity conducted on canonical lid-driven cavity and rotating annulus benchmarks prior to pump simulations.",
    "activityType": "CodeVerification",
