    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predictions are within acceptance criteria for pressure head (4.2% error), velocity field (6.8% NRMSE), and relative hemolysis index (within 95% CI). Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
